Project Description

Features:

Feed Tracker is an easy feed tracker that can be used for keeping your feeds up-to-date.

Supports:

  • RSS 2.0 and Atom 1.0 (other version will come soon)

New features to come:

  • Improved post summary.
  • Improved feed management.
  • New skin.
  • View original post in own built-in browser.
  • Multi-threading support.
